---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<h1>Dev Blog</h1>
				<p class="tagline">
					실무에서 바로 쓸 수 있는 개발 지식을 공유합니다
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="intro">
				<h2>Welcome</h2>
				<p>
					안녕하세요! 이 블로그는 프론트엔드, 백엔드, DevOps 등
					다양한 개발 분야의 실용적인 지식을 다루는 기술 블로그입니다.
				</p>
				<p>
					복잡한 개념도 쉽게 풀어서 설명하고, 실제 프로젝트에서
					바로 활용할 수 있는 코드와 팁을 공유하고 있어요.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="topics">
				<h2>Topics</h2>
				<ul class="topic-list">
					<li>
						<span class="topic-icon">Frontend</span>
						<span>React, Vue, TypeScript, Next.js</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span class="topic-icon">Backend</span>
						<span>Node.js, Python, Java, Go</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span class="topic-icon">DevOps</span>
						<span>Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span class="topic-icon">Database</span>
						<span>SQL, NoSQL, ORM</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="cta">
				<a href="/blog" class="cta-button">Blog</a>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2em 1em;
	}

	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3em 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 3em;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.2em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin: 0;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5em;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.5em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		padding-bottom: 0.3em;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--black));
	}

	p {
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
	}

	.topic-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 1em;
	}

	.topic-list li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1em;
		padding: 1em;
		background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.topic-icon {
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.85em;
		padding: 0.3em 0.8em;
		background: rgb(var(--black));
		color: white;
		border-radius: 4px;
		min-width: 80px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2em 0;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1em 3em;
		background: rgb(var(--black));
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		opacity: 0.8;
		color: white;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.2em;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 1em;
		}
	}
</style>
